2020年8月9日，若潮号运营商商船三井和该船所有者长铺汽船公司分别向毛里求斯致歉，日本已派出工作组协助模里西斯方处理善后事宜<ref name=":0" />。

=== 国际及其他国家 ===
[[绿色和平组织|绿色和平组织]]指出，本次漏油事故可能是“在小岛国出现的最可怕的生态危机之一”<ref name="france2">{{Cite web|title=Oil spill threatens ecological disaster as Mauritius declares emergency|url=https://news.yahoo.com/france-offers-aid-mauritius-declares-122144531.html|accessdate=2020-08-08|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=Reuters|language=|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629190337/https://news.yahoo.com/france-offers-aid-mauritius-declares-122144531.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於事故發生一年後的回顧中批評毛里裘斯政府處理事件的手法，包括無視環保團體的建議，倉卒決定在鯨魚哺育海域鑿沉若潮號的前半段；包庇船公司，拒絕向公眾透露重要資訊，包括洩漏的原油種類、為何選擇鑿沉而不把船體拖走拆解等；以及缺乏生態危害評估，不公開附近海岸發現的鯨魚及海豚屍體的檢驗報告結果，而事發地點直至現在仍不向科學家、[[非營利組織|非營利組織]]或媒體開放。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Bruneau Laurette, Rama Valayden, Melita Steele, Hisayo Takada |title=Mauritius one year after oil disaster |url=https://www.greenpeace.org/international/story/49085/mauritius-worst-environmental-disaster-one-year-on/ |website=綠色和平 |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119010820/https://www.greenpeace.org/international/story/49085/mauritius-worst-environmental-disaster-one-year-on/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[法国总统|法国总统]][[马克龙|马克龙]]发[[Twitter|推文]]回应贾格纳特的请求说<ref>{{cite web |title=Mauritius declares emergency as stranded ship spills fuel |url=https://news.yahoo.com/mauritius-asks-france-help-stranded-190514271.html |website=news.yahoo.com |publisher=Associated Press |author=Cara Anna |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114200251/https://news.yahoo.com/mauritius-asks-france-help-stranded-190514271.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：“当[[生物多样性|生物多样性]]处于危险之中时，就必须采取行动。法国在这里，与毛里求斯人民并肩作战。亲爱的贾格纳特，你可以指望我们的支持。”（{{lang|en|When biodiversity is in peril, there is urgency to act. France is there. Alongside the people of Mauritius. You can count on our support dear Jugnauth.}}）
